            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="disclaimer">
            DISCLAIMER: As per the rules of the Bar Council of India, legal practitioners are not permitted to solicit work or advertise. The information provided on this website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal advice or an invitation for a lawyer-client relationship.
